convenienceStoreMessage.title: convenienceStoreMessage
convenienceStoreMessage.value:
Please pay at the designated convenience store within 14 days from the next day of the order. After confirming payment, we will send an e-mail notifying you of the completion of purchase to your e-mail address.

Please refer to https://www.econtext.jp/support/cvs/6brand.html for details on payment methods at each convenience store. Once your order has been processed, a confirmation email will be sent to your registered email address.
